- It's good to see you.

1448
01:52:22,423 --> 01:52:24,254
I don't know why I'm here.

1449
01:52:24,859 --> 01:52:26,622
I got a lot of hate.

1450
01:52:27,428 --> 01:52:28,690
I don't have your faith.

1451
01:52:29,130 --> 01:52:31,758
It's not faith.
I wish it were that easy.

1452
01:52:32,700 --> 01:52:34,224
It's work.

1453
01:52:36,403 --> 01:52:37,665
Maybe...

1454
01:52:40,040 --> 01:52:44,033
...we could help each other find
a way out of the hate.

1455
01:52:46,714 --> 01:52:48,045
I don't know.

1456
01:52:49,683 --> 01:52:51,275
I don't think so.

1457
01:52:55,189 --> 01:52:56,588
I should go.

1458
01:53:14,074 --> 01:53:15,234
Evening.

1459
01:53:15,476 --> 01:53:17,034
- Good evening.
- Good evening.

